title: Fenerbahçe draw against Celtic in away match
text:
Fenerbahçe draw against Celtic in away match ANADOLU AGENCY ADD A MESSAGE YOUR E-MAIL 
Fenerbahçe snatched a draw against the Scottish club, Celtic, in the UEFA Europa League Group A match in Glasgow on Thursday. Celtic took the lead in their home Celtic Park when Scottish forward Leigh Griffiths found the net in the 28th minute, 1-0. Scottish team doubled the gap four minutes later as Scottish midfielder Kris Commons scored, 2-0. Visitors Fenerbahçe's Brazilian striker Fernandao narrowed the gap near the end of the first half, 1-2. In the 48th minute of the second half, Fernandao equalized the level in Glasgow, 2-2. Meanwhile, in the other match of Group A, Dutch club Ajax drew against Norway's Molde 1-1 in Norway. - Results of Group A: Celtic 2-2 Fenerbahçe Molde 1-1 Ajax Having four points, Molde are leading the group. Ajax come in second as they have two points as well as Celtic. Fenerbahçe are in fourth spot with a point.
